00:19:29,287 --> 00:19:32,120  X1:000 X2:719 Y1:002 Y2:574
BeforeJoseph was born?
Before we ever got married?

168
00:19:36,287 --> 00:19:38,198  X1:000 X2:719 Y1:002 Y2:574
