that's kind ofweird...

170
00:19:42,327 --> 00:19:46,320  X1:000 X2:719 Y1:002 Y2:574
not remembering one cold
or a-a fever or a sore throat?

171
00:19:48,527 --> 00:19:50,438  X1:000 X2:719 Y1:002 Y2:574
What do you think it means?

172
00:19:55,007 --> 00:19:57,805  X1:000 X2:719 Y1:002 Y2:574
Um...

173
00:19:57,887 --> 00:20:01,596  X1:000 X2:719 Y1:002 Y2:574
