because I break like glass.

181
00:21:13,047 --> 00:21:14,958  X1:000 X2:719 Y1:002 Y2:574
You make this decision now...

182
00:21:16,327 --> 00:21:18,238  X1:000 X2:719 Y1:002 Y2:574
to be afraid...

183
00:21:19,807 --> 00:21:21,877  X1:000 X2:719 Y1:002 Y2:574
and you will never turn back.

184
00:21:23,527 --> 00:21:28,157  X1:000 X2:719 Y1:002 Y2:574
Your whole life,
you will always be afraid.

185
00:21:42,367 --> 00:21:44,801  X1:000 X2:719 Y1:002 Y2:574
- I got a present foryou.
- Why?

186
00:21:46,447 --> 00:21:48,358  X1:000 X2:719 Y1:002 Y2:574
Forget why.

187
00:21:50,847 --> 00:21:52,758  X1:000 X2:719 Y1:002 Y2:574
You want it or not?

188
00:21:55,607 --> 00:21:57,723  X1:000 X2:719 Y1:002 Y2:574
Well, go get it, then.

189
00:21:57,807 --> 00:22:00,640  X1:000 X2:719 Y1:002 Y2:574
Where is it?

190
00:22:00,727 --> 00:22:03,241  X1:000 X2:719 Y1:002 Y2:574
On a bench...

191
00:22:03,327 --> 00:22:05,238  X1:000 X2:719 Y1:002 Y2:574
across the street.

192
00:22:18,727 --> 00:22:20,638  X1:000 X2:719 Y1:002 Y2:574
Someone's gonna take it.

193
00:22:22,567 --> 00:22:25,206  X1:000 X2:719 Y1:002 Y2:574
Then you better get out there soon.

194
00:23:36,607 --> 00:23:38,518  X1:000 X2:719 Y1:002 Y2:574
I bought a whole bunch.

195
00:23:42,847 --> 00:23:44,838  X1:000 X2:719 Y1:002 Y2:574
There'll be one ofthese
waitin' foryou...

196
00:23:44,927 --> 00:23:46,997  X1:000 X2:719 Y1:002 Y2:574
every time you want
to come out here.

197
00:23:53,447 --> 00:23:56,439  X1:000 X2:719 Y1:002 Y2:574
They say this one
has a surprise ending.

198
00:24:04,967 --> 00:24:07,879  X1:000 X2:719 Y1:002 Y2:574
This is from Fritz Campion's
own library.

199
00:24:07,967 --> 00:24:12,677  X1:000 X2:719 Y1:002 Y2:574
This is before the fiîrst issue of
the comic book hit the stands in 1 968.

200
00:24:12,767 --> 00:24:16,646  X1:000 X2:719 Y1:002 Y2:574
