of good versus evil.

201
00:24:16,727 --> 00:24:20,561  X1:000 X2:719 Y1:002 Y2:574
Notice the squarejaw ofSlayer,
common in most comic heroes.

202
00:24:20,647 --> 00:24:24,242  X1:000 X2:719 Y1:002 Y2:574
And the slightly disproportionate size
ofJaguaro's head to his body.

203
00:24:24,327 --> 00:24:28,240  X1:000 X2:719 Y1:002 Y2:574
This again is common,
but only in villains.

204
00:24:28,327 --> 00:24:30,636  X1:000 X2:719 Y1:002 Y2:574
The thing to notice about this piece...

205
00:24:30,727 --> 00:24:34,561  X1:000 X2:719 Y1:002 Y2:574
the thing that makes it
very, very special...

206
00:24:34,647 --> 00:24:37,605  X1:000 X2:719 Y1:002 Y2:574
