302
00:30:21,927 --> 00:30:24,760  X1:000 X2:719 Y1:002 Y2:574
"I just need
your credit card number...

303
00:30:24,847 --> 00:30:26,758  X1:000 X2:719 Y1:002 Y2:574
a small down payment."

304
00:30:29,327 --> 00:30:31,238  X1:000 X2:719 Y1:002 Y2:574
This morning was the fiîrst morning
that I could remember...

305
00:30:31,327 --> 00:30:33,238  X1:000 X2:719 Y1:002 Y2:574
that I didn't open my eyes
and feel...

306
00:30:35,967 --> 00:30:38,003  X1:000 X2:719 Y1:002 Y2:574
sadness.

307
00:30:41,447 --> 00:30:44,484  X1:000 X2:719 Y1:002 Y2:574
I thought the person that wrote
that note had an answer for me.

308
00:30:51,127 --> 00:30:54,039  X1:000 X2:719 Y1:002 Y2:574
I'm gonna leave now.

309
00:30:54,127 --> 00:30:56,038  X1:000 X2:719 Y1:002 Y2:574
Good luck with your exhibition.

310
00:30:56,127 --> 00:30:58,516  X1:000 X2:719 Y1:002 Y2:574
So, what kind ofjob
do you have, David?

311
00:30:58,607 --> 00:31:00,563  X1:000 X2:719 Y1:002 Y2:574
You said you've met guys like me
in your work.

312
00:31:00,647 --> 00:31:05,038  X1:000 X2:719 Y1:002 Y2:574
- What exactly is it that you do?
