314
00:33:17,727 --> 00:33:19,843  X1:000 X2:719 Y1:002 Y2:574
Hi.

315
00:33:19,927 --> 00:33:22,646  X1:000 X2:719 Y1:002 Y2:574
I've come to a decision.

316
00:33:22,727 --> 00:33:25,002  X1:000 X2:719 Y1:002 Y2:574
Okay.

317
00:33:25,087 --> 00:33:27,521  X1:000 X2:719 Y1:002 Y2:574
