320
00:33:37,047 --> 00:33:39,720  X1:000 X2:719 Y1:002 Y2:574
Have you been with anyone?

321
00:33:39,807 --> 00:33:41,957  X1:000 X2:719 Y1:002 Y2:574
I mean, since we've
been having problems.

322
00:33:42,047 --> 00:33:43,958  X1:000 X2:719 Y1:002 Y2:574
