324
00:33:49,687 --> 00:33:51,598  X1:000 X2:719 Y1:002 Y2:574
I mean, it won't affect me
either way.

325
00:33:53,927 --> 00:33:55,838  X1:000 X2:719 Y1:002 Y2:574
No.

326
00:34:03,407 --> 00:34:05,557  X1:000 X2:719 Y1:002 Y2:574
