856
01:33:23,285 --> 01:33:26,277  X1:000 X2:719 Y1:002 Y2:574
Mm-hmm. They were bad...

857
01:33:27,365 --> 01:33:29,799  X1:000 X2:719 Y1:002 Y2:574
